sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor Admin as ChuToChuc_Admin
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant OrgSvc as OrganizationService
participant ChannelDb as Mongo_Channel

Note over Admin,ChannelDb: Chặng 2 - Soft delete và lỗi quyền
Admin->>Gateway: DELETE /api/.../channels/:id
Gateway->>OrgSvc: Validate role owner/admin
alt Có quyền
  OrgSvc->>ChannelDb: Set isActive=false
  OrgSvc-->>Admin: 200
else Không có quyền
  OrgSvc-->>Admin: 403
end

Admin->>Gateway: PUT /api/.../departments/:id
alt Department không tồn tại
  OrgSvc-->>Admin: 404
else Cập nhật thành công
  OrgSvc-->>Admin: 200
end
